(46935, 128857, 4320, 4, '沈默/Silence', '', '2012-03-16 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 1, 7, '可不可以請妳別再關在妳的沈默 \r\n因為當妳結凍有人在聯想種淹沒 \r\n內心的怪物都被吵醒 \r\n於是勸妳嘗試另一種方式來滅火 \r\n\r\n快說出煩惱 \r\n或永遠住口 \r\n就是如果在暗處傷害了我的心 \r\n\r\n不管是什麼原因 \r\n無論妳故意與否 \r\n即使我不忍心 \r\n也將妳隔離 \r\n來向妳 \r\n報仇 \r\n\r\n如果妳是將我言語看成噪音 \r\n要告訴妳沈默不為金 \r\n而是能夠使人承受最殘忍的折磨 \r\n\r\n再也聽不到 \r\n向著妳開口 \r\n或許能教妳怎麼對下個人的心 \r\n\r\n否則妳就持續安靜吧 \r\n盡可能冷漠 \r\n浪費一生也行 \r\n至於我當成 \r\n妳不存在過 \r\n\r\nbut i''m a coward \r\ni won''t ever take that step \r\ni''ll be hanging to your lips \r\nuntil you deign to say a word \r\n\r\nwhy prolong this very dull moment \r\nrather than just telling me where i''ve erred \r\n\r\nand if you ask me \r\nwhat motivates such an anger \r\ni''ll say because i''ve got so much to lose \r\neach second''s a reminder \r\n\r\nthat someday what i''ve always imagined \r\nwill inevitably occur \r\n\r\nstop resorting to silence \r\ncease inflicting your absence on me \r\nsettling scores with words \r\nremember i am not your enemy \r\n\r\n怎可能將憤怒壓抑而過癮 \r\n\r\nstop resorting to silence \r\ncease inflicting your absence on me \r\nsettling scores with words \r\nremember i am not your enemy \r\n\r\n是不是從來不曾害怕失去我', '', 470, '', '胡月', '胡月', '胡月', '', '', 1, 1, 0, '2012-05-04 02:25:20', '2015-03-12 13:51:58', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(46936, 128857, 4320, 5, 'Reunion (重逢)', '', '2012-03-16 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 1, 7, 'the air is colored \r\nmist without thickness \r\nit''s comfort to the eye \r\n\r\nit''s warming my whole body \r\ni''m entirely here \r\nyet watching from afar \r\n\r\nyou were gone so long Dear \r\nit felt like eternity \r\ni''d never thought you''d come back \r\nand yet here you are \r\nsmiling at me \r\nwas it just a nightmare? \r\n\r\nhold on \r\ni cannot remember \r\nwhere i was a minute ago \r\n\r\ni don''t know how i''ve gotten here \r\nwas i never \r\nanywhere before? \r\n\r\nyou were gone so long Dear \r\nit felt like eternity \r\ni''d never thought you''d come back \r\nand yet here i am \r\nlooking into your eyes \r\nbut say \r\nwhere are we? \r\n\r\ni have overdue \r\napologies for you Dear \r\nso you hold no anger \r\npast is past let''s treasure now \r\n\r\nkeep walking close to me \r\ncloser please you never know \r\ni''ve got the oddest hunch \r\n\r\nthat in the twinkling of an eye \r\nyou could disappear \r\nleaving me forever alone \r\n\r\nwhat is going on Dear? \r\nthe mist has faded away \r\nand though you''re still around \r\ni can no longer cross \r\nthe space between us \r\nbut wait \r\ni''m dreaming... \r\n\r\n(Chinese translation: \r\n\r\n空氣被蒙上一片色彩 \r\n薄薄的雲霧輕柔無感 \r\n著實令雙眼感到舒緩 \r\n\r\n而溫暖了我的全身 \r\n即使我已全然在這兒 \r\n卻像從遠處望著這一切 \r\n\r\n妳已離開很久，親愛的 \r\n感覺像是永遠 \r\n我從未想過妳會回來 \r\n然而妳卻在這兒 \r\n對我笑著 \r\n難道過去只是場惡夢？ \r\n\r\n等等 \r\n我想不起來 \r\n前一分鐘的我在哪 \r\n\r\n我不知道我如何到達這裡 \r\n之前的我 \r\n曾在任何地方嗎？ \r\n\r\n妳已離開很久，親愛的 \r\n感覺像是永恆 \r\n我從沒想過妳會回來 \r\n而我卻在這兒 \r\n直視著妳的雙眼 \r\n但是 \r\n我們在哪裡？ \r\n\r\n我那時來不及 \r\n向妳道歉，親愛的 \r\n所以妳都不氣了嗎？ \r\n過去的就讓它過去嗎？我們珍惜現在 \r\n\r\n請繼續走在我身旁 \r\n再靠近一些，妳不會知道 \r\n我有個奇妙的預感 \r\n\r\n在妳眨眼瞬間 \r\n妳將隨時可能消失 \r\n永遠的離我而去 \r\n\r\n怎麼了？親愛的 \r\n霧氣已漸漸散去 \r\n而儘管妳還在 \r\n我已無法再跨越 \r\n我們之間的距離 \r\n但是，等一下 \r\n我在夢裡⋯）', '', 217, '', '胡月', '胡月（翻譯：YEAH!）', '胡月', '', '', 1, 1, 0, '2012-05-04 02:26:12', '2015-03-12 13:51:58', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
